#! @Description
#!  The arguments are two objects <A>a</A>, <A>b</A> and a tensor product algebroid <A>T</A>$=A\otimes B$ where <A>a</A> and <A>b</A> belong to $A$ resp. $B$.
#!  The output is the object $a\otimes b$ in <A>T</A>.
